readme: # Ganymede Atom Syntax A color scheme for Atom inspired by the icy coldness of the moons of Jupiter contrasted against all the bright vibrant colors that my personality comprises. ## Installation ``` apm install ganymede-atom-syntax ``` ## Colors ![Color Palette for Ganymede](assets/ganymede-palette.png) In use ![A screenshot of your theme](assets/screenshot-atom.png)
